								<h3><img src="/education/worldwar2/theatre-assets/mediterranean/where-will-allies-invade/safe/patricia-davies.jpg" alt="Patricia Trehearne (now Davies)" style="float:right;" />Transcript<br />Extract from a filmed interview with Patricia Trehearne (now Davies) made in 2007</h3>
